dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of approximately 1.5 million unstable and stable inorganic structures, used for training machine learning models to predict material properties.
dcterms:title: Materials Project Trajectory Dataset

dcterms:description: A diverse set of 55 stable structures selected from the Materials Project database, used as a benchmark for evaluating the performance of the proposed crystal structure prediction algorithm.
dcterms:title: Benchmark Set of 55 Stable Structures
